---
title: Asian Beef & Peanut Larb with Veggies & Garlic Rice
description: A 'salad' dish for meat lovers, larb is a Southeast Asian salad based on minced meat. In our Vietnamese-inspired version, we've bulked it up with fragrant jasmine rice, and flavoured the juicy beef mince with fish sauce, soy sauce and ginger and lemongrass for the perfect balance of bold flavours.
